// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4325 — Mass File Rename (ransomexx)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3592f1fa-ad35-59ce-9418-e104507716ef

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
